This is the README file for encoding::warnings, a module to
ease detection of "implicit encoding conversions" in Perl 5.8.0
and later.

Please type "perldoc encoding::warnings" after installation to see
the module usage information.

* Installation

encoding::warnings uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

